"{\"uid\": \"v1015.iheart.com-content-2024-08-02-rapper-flavor-flav-hopes-others-with-sponsor-olympic-teams\", \"text\": \"Rap icon Flavor Flav is in Paris cheering on the USA women's water polo team. The New York native is sponsoring the team and he told the Today Show, he hopes other celebrities follow his lead. Flav says it costs a lot of money to train and many athletes have two or three jobs to help with their finances. Flavor Flav, by the way, calls himself the water polo team's \\\"Hype Man  Photo:Clive Rose / Getty Images Sport / Getty Images\"}"